data.description: Wonderful all-one-floor ranch home! This 3 bedroom, one and a half bath home is perfect for single level living. Features a large eat in kitchen, three spacious bedrooms (one currently used as an office) and a handicapped equipped bathroom with both bathtub and roll-in shower. Quiet location with a lush side lot, garage(with attic) and two sheds. All new hardwood flooring and freshly painted. Add your own polish to make it yours.
